metadata.description:
"Ha ha ha, captain Zhang, hard, really hard, don't get up, your body is not good, then lie down!" Xu Yaoqian smiled and came over, gently hold zhang Tianhao will get up, softly said.



Zhang Tianhao immediately looked at Xu Key with gratitude, excited said: "Stationmaster, are subordinate I incompetent......"



"Ha ha, you have done very well, even suffering from a serious illness, but also the heart of the party state, is really the model of the party state, the elite of the party state!"



Then he grasped Zhang tianhao's hands tightly and said seriously, "This time, you were framed by those people. There were eight of you, except for Xiao Hou and Luo Zhong, who were on duty. Otherwise, you would have confessed to them all. They are too rampant. When you get better, you must crack down on their arrogance."
